<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6d783549249270da985a6e82c51ed5b234b74c","tid":2489825,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"28 歲工程師被指在 Telegram 頻道中，教導他人「焗死」水炮車上的警員，以及破壞交通燈等，遭控五罪，還押至今逾 10 個月。案件今（15日）在區域法院提訊，被告否認所有控罪。法官李慶年押後案件至 2022 年 2 月 21 日開審，審期為 7 日。控方表示將傳召專家證人，講解Telegram 運作和術語。<br />\n<br />\n被告否認所有控罪，控方表示將傳召 6 位警員，以及 1 位有關 Telegram 訊息和術語的專家證人。法官質疑為何要傳召 Telegram 術語專家，笑指「我哋唔係審黑社會案喎」而需要術語專家。控方回覆，專家將講解 Telegram 運作。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露需時外聘律師處理本案。案件押後至 2022 年 2 月 21 日開審，審期為 7 日。被告無保釋申請，須要繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-tg-%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%AD%89%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%94%E7%BD%AA-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%B8%8D%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%93%AC%E5%82%B3-tg-%E8%A1%93%E8%AA%9E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-tg-%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%2582%25B3-tg-%25E8%25A1%2593%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sCQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=079be9f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-tg-%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%2582%25B3-tg-%25E8%25A1%2593%25E8%25AA%259E%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=39ee3533\" data-a